Parameter.Name: LineFilterRetransMaxGapSize
Parameter.Comment: Max number of messages per request, defined the exchange side

Parameter.Name: TsxRetransMaxQueueSize
Parameter.Comment: Maximum retrans queue size to keep. Older retrans request will be discarded if this limit is reached. Set to 0 to have no limit.

Parameter.Name: TsxMaxRetransMsgsPerRequest
Parameter.Comment: Maximum retrans gap size supported per request.

Parameter.Name: MhIfOrderBookUniqueOrderIds
Parameter.Comment: This must be set to false if order book is used.

Feed.Name: tl2_cdf_alp
Feed.Comment: This parameter (Tl2IsAlpha) must be set to false or deleted before for the switch over to the new Alpha feed on TMX. After the switch the alpha subfeed will follow the same rules as tsx.
